From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 08:54:40 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Route navigation state

Pane names point to engine tabs,
Stale ghosts are waved away.
The browser whispers can and cannot,
And Ghostty keeps the map in play.
---
